{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2647900/extras/About_Seth.png?t=1740668331\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take control of <strong>Seth</strong>, god of the desert, on his quest to fight Apophis. In a game where Fast-FPS meets Rogue-Lite, battle waves of brutal enemies and ruthless bosses. <strong>Choose your weapon, fight, die, and rise again!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2647900/extras/power.gif?t=1740668331\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2647900/extras/high_risks_high_rewards.gif?t=1740668331\" /></h2></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into battle with a <strong>shield mechanic that encourages risk-taking</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Slay your foes, tear their soul apart from their body to replenish your shield and resist the most powerful attacks. But <strong>act quickly and stay close</strong> to them before they reach the underworld.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2647900/extras/shield.gif?t=1740668331\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2647900/extras/play_style_eng.gif?t=1740668331\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from a selection of <strong>weapons with unique abilities</strong>, such as a slowdown for the bow or a grappling hook on your shotgun. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use them alongside your melee skills, dash, and spells to defeat your enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2647900/extras/hook.gif?t=1740668331\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2647900/extras/death_is_only_the_beginning.gif?t=1740668331\" />Each god have their own style. <strong>Receive their powers, combine them</strong> and make each one of your run unique. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Between two runs, restore your divinity to become the feared god you used to be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2647900/extras/b\u00e9n\u00e9dictions_eng.gif?t=1740668331\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2647900?t=1740668331","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2647900/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740668331","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2647900/c7d7b88e9c2396cec12a432d67fff966b924e08a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740668331","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2647900/c7d7b88e9c2396cec12a432d67fff966b924e08a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740668331","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"Seth focuses on intense fights against humanoid, non-humanoid and fantastic creatures, with firearms and melee. The game contains also strong language."},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2647900/extras/About_Seth.png?t=1740668331\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take control of <strong>Seth</s